08:25:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/state-prosecutor-calling-arab-lawmakers-terrorists-constitutes-protected-speech/00000190-7216-d0bf-a9fd-76fe366f0000</guid></item><item><title>反对党领袖拉皮德称内塔尼亚胡计划解雇以色列总检察长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-says-netanyahu-planning-to-fire-israels-ag/00000190-720d-d129-afba-ffffb6570000</link><description>极右翼部长大卫·阿姆萨勒姆指责司法部长“竭尽全力推翻政府”。拉皮德警告内塔尼亚胡正在考虑解雇总检察长，并告诉他的政党的立法者，不排除任何选择，包括集体辞职</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:22:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-says-netanyahu-planning-to-fire-israels-ag/00000190-720d-d129-afba-ffffb6570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何应对勒庞领导的全国集会党可能赢得的极右翼法国大选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-is-contending-with-a-potential-far-right-french-election-win-by-le-pens-party/00000190-6fe7-dbfd-a5d1-eff783700000</link><description>以色列现在需要权衡法国极右翼目前对以色列的立场、其反犹太主义根源以及法国犹太社区对其民族主义言论的恐惧，因为几十年来一直拒绝与法国极右翼建立任何官方关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/how-israel-is-contending-with-a-potential-far-right-french-election-win-by-le-pens-party/00000190-6fe7-dbfd-a5d1-eff783700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队准备结束加沙战斗，但未达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-set-to-wind-down-fighting-in-gaza-but-without-reaching-a-hostage-deal/00000190-6f9a-d0bf-a9fd-6ffa14f20000</link><description>关键问题将是如何让公众相信以色列已经实现了战争期间的目标，尽管哈马斯尚未被彻底击败，而且 120 名人质仍滞留在加沙。 ■ 以色列领导人对 Al-Shifa 获释一事进行指责医院院长，内塔尼亚胡时代的惨败象征</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 03:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-set-to-wind-down-fighting-in-gaza-but-without-reaching-a-hostage-deal/00000190-6f9a-d0bf-a9fd-6ffa14f20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，两名以色列士兵在加沙中部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-live/netanyahu-says-israel-close-to-eliminating-hamas-military/00000190-713b-d33f-a7b9-75bfb46f0000</link><description>以色列国防军呼吁巴勒斯坦人撤离汗尤尼斯东部社区 ■ 内塔尼亚胡办公室表示，政府并不知道释放 Al-Shifa 医院院长的决定 ■ 梅图拉的房屋遭到火箭袭击 ■ 西班牙要求加入国际法院对以色列的种族灭绝指控 ■ Gallant称以色列军队立即需要1万名士兵</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 02:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article-live/netanyahu-says-israel-close-to-eliminating-hamas-military/00000190-713b-d33f-a7b9-75bfb46f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院以色列新法官抨击种族灭绝听证会“在思想上不诚实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</link><description>佩雷斯学术中心院长罗恩·夏皮拉教授被吹捧为现任政府可能任命的最高法院法官，政府希望任命一名保守派法官</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 21:31:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-judge-at-icj-slammed-genocide-hearing-as-intellectually-dishonest/00000190-7027-d33f-a7b9-74b7be7f0000</guid></item><item><title>青少年被以色列国防军招募从事情报行动，然后因间谍活动被判入狱，起诉国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/teen-recruited-by-idf-for-intelligence-operation-then-jailed-for-espionage-sues-state/00000190-6fd6-d705-a7f5-ffffc0890000</link><description>双桅船。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的新任军事部长罗曼·戈夫曼将军批准在一场“影响力运动”中使用这名 16 岁男孩。在针对国家提起的诉讼中，该青少年声称他在拘留期间受到虐待</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 20:27:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/teen-recruited-by-idf-for-intelligence-operation-then-jailed-for-espionage-sues-state/00000190-6fd6-d705-a7f5-ffffc0890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布，以色列国防军士兵在约旦河西岸军事行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-during-west-bank-military-operation/00000190-6e6b-d6fc-afba-ef7bfd000000</link><description>在约旦河西岸城市图尔卡尔姆附近的努尔沙姆斯难民营的夜间行动中，一辆军车下爆炸装置引爆，造成一名以色列士兵死亡，另一名以色列士兵重伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 19:37:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/idf-soldier-killed-during-west-bank-military-operation/00000190-6e6b-d6fc-afba-ef7bfd000000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和勒庞的教训：以色列中左翼合并如何阻止极右翼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-01/ty-article/.highlight/lessons-from-netanyahu-and-le-pen-how-israels-center-left-merger-can-halt-the-far-right/00000190-6f56-d0bf-a9fd-6ffe924c0000</link><description>以色列工党与左翼梅雷茨的合并，是左翼和中间派如何抵制独裁民族主义浪潮的起点和蓝图</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 18:03:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-01/ty-article/.highlight/lessons-from-netanyahu-and-le-pen-how-israels-center-left-merger-can-halt-the-far-right/00000190-6f56-d0bf-a9fd-6ffe924c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-6f36-dbfd-a5d1-efb717810000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，中士。来自贝尔谢巴的 21 岁男子奥里·伊茨查克·哈达 (Ori Itzchak Hadad) 在爆炸中丧生。另有一名士兵在事件中受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:18:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-southern-gaza-idf-announces/00000190-6f36-dbfd-a5d1-efb717810000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡总理私人住宅附近的耶路撒冷市中心街道大门施工开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/construction-on-gate-blocking-jerusalem-street-near-pm-netanyahus-private-home-begins/00000190-6f2c-d9e6-af9d-6ffefb5a0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷私人住宅旁边的永久大门可用于封锁整条街道，近几个月来，该地区一直是反政府抗议活动的场所，抗议活动要求释放在加沙被扣押的人质</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/construction-on-gate-blocking-jerusalem-street-near-pm-netanyahus-private-home-begins/00000190-6f2c-d9e6-af9d-6ffefb5a0000</guid></item><item><title>报道：以色列士兵在加沙使用被拘留者作为“人体盾牌”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/report-israeli-soldiers-filmed-using-detainees-in-gaza-as-human-shields/00000190-6f2b-d6fc-afba-ef7b8ad20000</link><description>半岛电视台发布的视频片段显示，士兵命令穿着以色列军装、身上安装有随身摄像机的巴勒斯坦人在士兵之前进入建筑物和隧道开口</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:10:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/report-israeli-soldiers-filmed-using-detainees-in-gaza-as-human-shields/00000190-6f2b-d6fc-afba-ef7b8ad20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 269 天：西班牙要求加入国际法院针对以色列的请愿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-269-spain-asks-to-join-icj-petition-against-israel/00000190-6f40-d9e6-af9d-6fd2e7830001</link><description>以色列释放了加沙 Al-Shifa 医院院长以及其他约 50 名巴勒斯坦人 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡和国防部长加兰特表示，他们并不了解这一决定 ■ 西班牙要求加入南非请愿书，在国际法院指控以色列犯下种族灭绝罪 ■ 斯莫特里奇称他批准了五个新的定居点，作为对单方面承认巴勒斯坦国的国家的回应 ■ 这是战争开始 269 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 17:09:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-269-spain-asks-to-join-icj-petition-against-israel/00000190-6f40-d9e6-af9d-6fd2e7830001</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女背着X走来走去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-women-in-israel-walking-around-with-an-x-on-their-back/00000190-5f34-d747-add0-dffddac50000</link><description>记者罗尼·辛格最近的电视报道透露，有一个新单位的存在，旨在帮助拯救遭到暗杀的以色列妇女。她解释了为什么现在唯一的解决方案是给他们在海外新的生活</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-women-in-israel-walking-around-with-an-x-on-their-back/00000190-5f34-d747-add0-dffddac50000</guid></item><item><title>加沙渔民声称自己的船只在战争中被毁，以色列拒绝退还押金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-denies-deposit-refund-to-gaza-fishermen-who-say-their-boats-were-destroyed-in-war/00000190-6e8e-d4b8-a7b9-fe8f2cb70000</link><description>战前因超出捕鱼界限而被扣押的两名渔民交了 4 万美元押金才取回船只。法院表示，他们必须提供船只受损情况的照片，但这是不可能的，因为他们逃到了加沙南部，无法返回北部</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 14:56:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-denies-deposit-refund-to-gaza-fishermen-who-say-their-boats-were-destroyed-in-war/00000190-6e8e-d4b8-a7b9-fe8f2cb70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在加沙海岸附近的浮动援助运送码头是否总是沉在水中？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/was-bidens-floating-aid-delivery-pier-off-the-gaza-coast-always-dead-in-the-water/00000190-6e48-d4b8-a7b9-fec9b4f30000</link><description>这个耗资 2.3 亿美元的浮动码头在加沙海岸附近的两个月内仅运营了 28 天。更糟糕的是，6500吨物资中的大部分仍在等待国际机构领取，而不是到达巴勒斯坦人手中</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:50:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/was-bidens-floating-aid-delivery-pier-off-the-gaza-coast-always-dead-in-the-water/00000190-6e48-d4b8-a7b9-fec9b4f30000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙地面上与以色列“幽灵部队”进行战斗，几乎不被人看到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-ground-in-gaza-with-israels-ghost-unit-fighting-already-8-months/00000190-6df8-d9e6-af9d-6ffa9f9f0000</link><description>多域部队的以色列士兵在加沙行动中使用机器人、无人机和机密仪器。当我们陪同他们在加沙市中心执行任务时，有一件事明显缺席</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 13:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-01/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-ground-in-gaza-with-israels-ghost-unit-fighting-already-8-months/00000190-6df8-d9e6-af9d-6ffa9f9f0000</guid></item><item><title>在特拉维夫举行的重大和平活动之前，以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在美国各地集会要求停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-cease-fire-israelis-and-palestinians-rally-across-u-s-ahead-of-tel-aviv-peace-event/00000190-6ddd-de49-ad95-ffddc9ab0000</link><description>周日，包括以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在内的数百名抗议者在北美各地城市举行抗议活动，呼吁结束战争、返回人质并支持特拉维夫的“现在是时候”和平集会</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 12:22:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-07-01/ty-article/.premium/pro-cease-fire-israelis-and-palestinians-rally-across-u-s-ahead-of-tel-aviv-peace-event/00000190-6ddd-de49-ad95-ffddc9ab0000</guid></item></channel></rss>